AB  - In this paper, the model for quality overall parameters design of the large complex product based on multi-participant collaborating is first proposed First, the quality-gain function is designed which considers that collaboration for the large complex product brings benefit on quality, then cost function are expressed and cost sharing way is given based on Shapley value method Next the grey target model applicable to unlimited strategies is proposed and the maximum minimization model for the off-target distance is established at the same time. Finally, a numerical study is used to verify the feasibility and reasonability of the model. The design way of quality overall parameters for the large complex product may give some suggestions for the manufacturer and his partners if they all focus more on the long-term strategic cooperation and the whole cooperative benefits rather than the short-term single income.
